## What is a "platform brains hub"?

This folder is **not a code repo**. It exists to hold the `.platform/` context pack that coordinates multiple sibling repos (for example, a backend + a frontend + a widget living in neighbouring folders). The hub is where cross-repo architecture, decisions, conventions, and workflow live so every AI session across every repo reads from the same source of truth.

You'll see folders next to this one like `../my-backend`, `../my-frontend`, `../my-widget` — those are the repos this hub coordinates. The hub itself holds only `.platform/`, this `CLAUDE.md`, and optionally a README.

